        <description>This holds the number of seconds the Pharmacy Card Lookup ID remains valid. This will be used to filter the PBM Plans that are listed in the Pharmacy Ebenefit Investigation workflow. If no value is provided, then it is assumed that the PBM Plans remain indefinitely valid.</description>
